#"Call Me Ishmael"
The Sperm Whale, a spouting fish with horizontal tail, is, without doubt, the largest inhabitant of the globe; the most formidable of all whales to encounter; the most majestic in aspect.

#"D3lph1nu5 h0dl1tu5"

#"Tribute to Idées Noires"

#"Minimalist Skulls"
Skeenee´s Minimalist Skull series showcases a series of skulls stripped down to their essential curves & shapes painted with a limited color scheme(3 colors) without gradients or shading techniques. 5 variations of different colors are available for each skull.

#"Classic Skulls"
Acrylic paintings of  skulls on rough linen canvas contrasting hot and cold colors.  "Skeenee´s Classics" series, traditional paintings on canvas tokenized on the Ethereum blockchain.
